AUDIO: 'where there\'s just music is the perfect time for a voiceover to happen. So, at this point I\'m super impressed and I want to throw a different theme at it. I basically just told chat to rewrite this with a steampunk theme, which it did. Still incorporating the logo, it gave us this.'

[04:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
