[05:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'missed the second I in the word mini, but you get the potential here. It created this huge metal structure based on the logo. I just love that. So, now I wanted to push it a little bit further. So, I brought this image here into chat, which is basically an image that I'

[05:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'created using Nano Banana 2 from the webpage of Openart and told it to turn it into a city, which it did. Then I said, "Let\'s do a version that takes the visual theme of this image, but with no reference to any text on the image cuz there\'s a lot of text on this image. It'

[05:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'should just be featuring Fish Audio and the title of the video will be the Fish Audio API." So, here it gives us our prompt. Throw all that in there and this is what we get. &gt;&gt; [music]'

[05:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; Crazy. By the way, as I record these, Seedance is still only available at'

