AUDIO: '720p, but 1080p is coming and can you imagine what that will do to this type of visual. So, it\'s about this time I got the thought, "I have to do a video on this." So, let\'s do some opening sequences about how good Seedance is. So, I brought my studio back in here for'

[06:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a visual reference and I said, "Let\'s do one for the Seedance 2 model using elements of what we know about the model because this whole conversation here is about the Seedance 2 model and how to prompt it good so it knows all of that. The title should be Seedance 2 and the'

[06:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'subtitle is "It\'s as good as they say" and referring to this image for the style. Here is our prompt and it gave us this. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; So again, all that part of the beginning'

[06:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is when I would have some sort of a voiceover talking about what we\'re going to talk about. Here\'s just another pass at that same prompt. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; That\'s when I realized I don\'t want the'

[07:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'subtitle to be "It\'s as good as they say" but instead let\'s have it say "Creating opening sequences" cuz that\'s what this whole video is about. &gt;&gt; [music]'

[07:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; I mean, the way the music accentuates everything, the use of the sound, it\'s just top level. So, you know how I\'ve been talking about the beginning would be a great time to have voiceover, but'

[07:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'then I thought, "Well, why don\'t I just use some reference images, tell it what to say, and do the voiceover right here on the screen?" The Seedance 2.0 model is out and now available for everyone globally. One of'

[07:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the more exciting use cases that people may not be taking advantage of is creating engaging opening sequences for your video like this one you\'re watching right now. &gt;&gt; And we created that prompt the exact same way as all the others. We came over here to chat and said, "Give me a version of this last one that features a'

[07:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'character whose face appears in the lower right-hand corner" and then gave it the script of what to say. This next example is a little different. I veered way off path of just doing the motion graphics and went into using real people. I was kind of hoping for more of a blend of real people and the motion'

[08:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'graphics and more illustrative things, but what I told it to do was to create an opening for a lifestyle show about taking care of your plants and animals in your home and looking for a fun montage sequence to open up the video. It created this prompt. I used these two'

[08:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'characters that I\'ve created here in the Openart platform to replace the man and the woman in the prompt and then we get this. And think about how you might use this'

